channel.title: ManzpkScape 614 UPDATED 8-26-2010
channel.description:
[b]Features:[/b] PVP (Must be level 10 for the PK Minimum Level) NPC Clipping Weapon Spec Full Map Player Clipping Logging In Running Walking Chat Commands Melee Mage Range NPC Combat NPC Dialogue Shops Bank Skills Clan Chat Added Party (Have Up to 4 members is a party to split exp/loot.) Removed Runes and Added Mana (Works same as prayer. Each spell takes off a little mana.) +More (Kinda tired so dont want to add everything it 12:32 am for me.)
[b]How to make your self owner:[/b] [code]Run the server Rune the Client Make an account Log in with the account Create a character Log in Go to the server panel Go to the players tab Click your name so that its highlighted To the right click player rights Change your rights to 5 for owner[/code]
[b]How to change the name on the client:[/b] [code]Go into the Server folder Click on the Data notepad Where it says GameName=GameName Change it to GameName=YourServerName[/code]
[b]How to change the IP Address:[/b] [code]Go to the Client Folder Find the Config notepad Where it says IP=127.0.0.1 Change it to IP=YourIPAddress[/code]
[b]Took Out Emote Tab Added A Suprise! How to do emotes:[/b] [code]Log into the game These are the commands for the emotes all 100% Custom: /cool /curse /blush /what /cry /:p /mad /:o /pause /devil[/code]
[b]Also I have made it to where there is no need for a compiler. Simply save and it is auto compiled![/b]
